<p>Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

<p>Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</p>

<p style="background-color: #d71845;
        border: none;
        color: white;
        padding: 15px 15px;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 12px;"><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), style: "color:white; text-decoration:none" %></p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>

<p style="font-style:italic">From the Wishlist team</p>